_:N5ff5b5c3fc9f4dc5845ecec071f810bc <http://schema.org/description> "The Government Recruitment Service (GRS) was launched in September 2017 and is part of the Cabinet Office’s Government People Group. GRS delivers award-winning recruitment services and functions for organisations across the Civil Service, supporting and enabling the recruitment of exceptional civil servants. GRS is part of the Government People Group ." .
